sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as POST /memory
    participant Validate as _validate_memory_input
    participant Classifier as MemoryClassifier
    participant Graph as FalkorDB
    participant EmbedQ as EmbeddingQueue
    participant Qdrant
    
    Client->>API: Store memory
    API->>Validate: Check fields
    Validate->>Classifier: Classify type (if not provided)
    Classifier-->>API: type + confidence
    
    API->>Graph: MERGE Memory node (immediate, blocking)
    Graph-->>API: memory_id
    
    alt Embedding provided
        API->>Qdrant: Upsert point + payload (immediate)
    else No embedding
        API->>EmbedQ: Enqueue for batch processing
    end
    
    API-->>Client: 201 Created + memory_id
    
    Note over EmbedQ,Qdrant: Background worker processes queue